noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;neuroscience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">111012343069497779</guid><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 11:38:43 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>PsychoPy</title><link>https://mastodon.social/@psychopy/111012430105984318</link><description>If you're attending &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mastodon.social/tags/BPSCOGDEV" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;BPSCOGDEV&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; next week we are running a workshop as part of the pre-conference event! Making eye tracking experiments with PsychoPy + Tobii üëÄ Register to attend here üëâ  &lt;a href="https://www.bps.org.uk/event/cognitive-and-developmental-preconference-networking-event" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://www.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;bps.org.uk/event/cognitive-and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;-developmental-preconference-networking-event&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; @bpsofficial @bpscognitive @bpsdevsection</description><guid isPermaLink="false">111012430105984318</guid><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 12:00:54 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Benjamin Han</title><link>https://sigmoid.social/@BenjaminHan/111008892193630279</link><description>Cade Metz‚Äôs NYTimes article on Doug Lenat, featuring quotes from Ken Forbus and &lt;span class="h-card"&gt;&lt;a class="u-url mention" href="https://sigmoid.social/@garymarcus" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;@&lt;span&gt;garymarcus&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. The connection between the game Traveller and &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://sigmoid.social/tags/Cyc" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Cyc&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is interesting and is new to me.Douglas Lenat, Who Tried to Make Computers More Human, Dies at 72 &lt;a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/09/04/technology/douglas-lenat-dead.html" rel="nofollow noope